Ext.data.JsonP['Appcelerator_CLI_4.1.3_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Appcelerator CLI 4.1.3 - 09 September 2015</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46239637\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Appcelerator CLI 4.1.3 - 09 September 2015</h1>\n    <p>Appcelerator CLI 4.1.3 is a patch release, addressing high-priority issues from previous releases.  This release of the Appcelerator CLI includes version 4.1.1 of the NPM package and version 4.1.3 of the Core package.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239637_AppceleratorCLI4.1.3ReleaseNote-ComponentVersions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Component Versions</span></h2>\n    <p>The following components are shipped with CLI 4.1.3:    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Name    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Version    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</thead><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Alloy    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>1.6.2    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \"><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Release_Notes\">Arrow Builder</a></strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \">1.2.48 (update)</strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \"><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Runtime_Services_Release_Notes\">Arrow Cloud CLI</a></strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \">1.0.26 (update)</strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Titanium CLI    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>4.0.1    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239637_AppceleratorCLI4.1.3ReleaseNote-FixedIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-766\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-766</a>: &quot;Missing required option: --id &lt;value&gt;&quot; error is returned if you specify all the required flags to create an app    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-767\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-767</a>: Cannot create a Titanium project &quot;appc new&quot;    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46239637\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Appcelerator CLI 4.1.3 Release Note"});